    "headline": "Packaging Corporation of America (NYSE:PKG) Misses Q1 CY2026 Sales Expectations",
    "summary": "Packaging Corporation of America (NYSE:PKG) fell short of the market’s revenue expectations in Q1 CY2026, but sales rose 10.6% year on year to $2.37 billion. Its GAAP profit of $1.91 per share was 9.4% below analysts’ consensus estimates.",
